    "description": "Voxelgram 2》是一款 3D 拼图逻辑游戏，在游戏中，你要通过拼凑体素模型并发现它们所形成的视角来解决谜题。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820620/extras/1148c2913a05556ae1fa60f18e57b3a5.poster.avif?t=1770799038\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820620/extras/1148c2913a05556ae1fa60f18e57b3a5.webm?t=1770799038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820620/extras/1148c2913a05556ae1fa60f18e57b3a5.mp4?t=1770799038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Voxelgram 2 提供了 250 个新谜题和一套全新的规则，现在有两种颜色可供选择。这些谜题被组织成 20 个手工制作的景观。<br></li><li>如果您拥有之前的Voxelgram游戏，您还可以访问原始谜题，这些谜题已被重新调整以符合新的双色规则。这意味着额外有250个谜题等你解决！<br></li><li>为了提供无限的可重玩性，游戏具有不同大小、形状和特征的程序生成谜题。<br></li><li>你还可以玩其他玩家创建的谜题，感谢Steam Workshop的支持。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820620/extras/8ed02b893e0dcc4c6a75af033e2c3979.avif?t=1770799038\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820620/extras_big/8ed02b893e0dcc4c6a75af033e2c3979.avif?t=1770799038 width=800 height=398 /></span>",
